<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DVNA-PFE — Dashboard Securise</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<main class="main-content">

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div>
        <div class="page-title">Dashboard</div>
        <div class="page-subtitle">Connecte en tant que <strong><%= user.username %></strong> — Role : <%= user.role %></div>
      </div>
      <span class="vuln-badge" style="background:rgba(45,186,114,.15);border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.3);color:#2dba72;">Version Securisee</span>
    </div>
    <div class="alert alert-success">
      Toutes les vulnerabilites ont ete corrigees dans cette version. Les modules ci-dessous fonctionnent de maniere securisee.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:500; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:12px;">
    Modules — Versions corrigees
  </div>

  <div class="vuln-grid">

    <a href="/ping" class="vuln-card" style="border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.2);">
      <div class="vuln-card-num" style="color:var(--green);">FIX-01</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Ping Tool</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool" style="color:var(--green);">Semgrep — SAST corrige</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">spawn() avec validation IPv4 stricte. Plus d'injection de commande possible.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/search" class="vuln-card" style="border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.2);">
      <div class="vuln-card-num" style="color:var(--green);">FIX-02</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Recherche utilisateur</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool" style="color:var(--green);">OWASP ZAP — DAST corrige</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">Echappement automatique via &lt;%= %&gt;. XSS impossible.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/notes" class="vuln-card" style="border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.2);">
      <div class="vuln-card-num" style="color:var(--green);">FIX-03</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Notes privees</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool" style="color:var(--green);">OWASP ZAP — IDOR corrige</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">Verification d'appartenance systematique. Acces refuse si la note n'est pas la votre.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/deserialize" class="vuln-card" style="border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.2);">
      <div class="vuln-card-num" style="color:var(--green);">FIX-04</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Deserialisation</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool" style="color:var(--green);">npm audit — SCA corrige</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">node-serialize supprime. JSON.parse() uniquement — pas d'execution de code.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/xml" class="vuln-card" style="border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.2);">
      <div class="vuln-card-num" style="color:var(--green);">FIX-05</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Parser XML</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool" style="color:var(--green);">Semgrep — XXE corrige</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">@xmldom/xmldom securise + rejet explicite de DOCTYPE et ENTITY.</div>
    </a>

    <div class="vuln-card" style="border-color:rgba(45,186,114,.2);cursor:default;">
      <div class="vuln-card-num" style="color:var(--green);">FIX-06</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">En-tetes HTTP</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool" style="color:var(--green);">OWASP ZAP — Headers corriges</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">helmet() active : CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, COEP, Referrer-Policy, Permissions-Policy.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
